BinderFactory, BinderFactoryWrapper, Component, GenericStateModel
public class PluginSanityBinder
extends ServiceFilter

A Binder for plugins which complains when various known-bad plugin behaviors are observed. Currently, it complains (at warn level) about non-local Tasks which are added or changed.
